### Get account by id
GET http://localhost:1024/api/v1/accounts/{{userId}}
Authorization: Basic {{adminBasic}}

### Card pagination
GET http://localhost:1024/api/v1/cards?page={{page}}&size={{size}}
Authorization: Basic {{adminBasic}}

